{%- comment -%}
  EYE Analytics — site-wide tracker.

  WHERE: Online Store → Themes → Edit code → layout/theme.liquid
  PASTE: just before the closing </head> tag.

  Replace the two placeholders below:
    __EYE_API_URL__  → your EYE backend/API URL (no trailing slash),
                       e.g. https://api.your-eye-domain.com
    __EYE_TOKEN__    → the data-token from your EYE domain settings
{%- endcomment -%}
<script async
        src="__EYE_API_URL__/tracker/eye.js"
        data-token="__EYE_TOKEN__"
        data-api="__EYE_API_URL__/api/track"></script>
